metadata.name: Salton Sea Revisited
metadata.description:
Award-winning time slice of the Salton Sea, created March 2012.

Permanent collection of Southern Utah Museum of Art.

ºInternational Photography Awards
ºWestmony Ridley-Tree Museum, Montecito, California
ºIEEE Viz Art Exhibit, Atlanta, Georgia
Published in:
ºLeonardo Journal of Arts, Sciences, and Technology. Volume 49. Issue 2. MIT Press. 2015.
ºSalton Sea Revisited: An Aesthetic Study of Realtime Lapse. Proceedings of the IEEE VIS Arts Program (VISAP). 2013.
